            <title>联想小新 Pro 14/16 2024 笔记本海外发布：搭载酷睿 Ultra 处理器，可选 RTX 4050 独显</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/739/333.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/739/333.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
